oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Unidentified girl by chair
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This image of an unidentified girl is from an old photograph album found at an estate sale. She wears a plaid dress with a hoop and saque coat, the same clothing worn by the boy - perhaps her brother - in wils004.; The children in wils003, wils004, wils005, wils006 appear to have been photographed in the same studio. The chair in this image is the same as the one in wils003.
